{"tid":1237264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（唔好鬆懈）呢幾日正苦派膠式記招發言 不代表香港人勝利","createTime":"2019-06-17T14:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T12:15:41.000Z","uid":261756,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a502ded046c2335f7b3294afacdae91c44d499f6","tid":1237264,"uid":261756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"標題<br />\n<br />\n係咁，個隻淋巴癌和綠帽蔥 輪流出泥派膠自打嘴巴，好似向香港人跪低左，但我覺得唔會咁撚順利，係佢地派膠個陣，大家都真是唔好因為佢地比小小甜頭大家就鬆懈，呢場係慢長的民主運動，我信大家應該都有相同的目標 1撤法 2撤罪 3問責 ，其實現在<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本無一樣係成功做到</span></span>，佢都係無正面肯定做到呢d野，所以<br />\n不撒不散  不責不散  港人治港 不忘今刻"},{"pid":"efeb2931f06582f829aacee4893df69bccead989","tid":1237264,"uid":261756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f22831840663cec9829403fb1643e23735acbd8","tid":1237264,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041b83159c05e777464ec56f9244383c4e1c2029","tid":1237264,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cb5767d5e852584be94ce7d4388527ed8245dd","tid":1237264,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T21:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc26bb0a6d97e66a1dcf66d8439f79713f67b4","tid":1237264,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9186e1a0d05837ea54895d7a5b46839b03f8548","tid":1237264,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}